 with the semiconductor-related\nprocedures may make this strategy widely applicable to various thin film\noptoelectronic devices. Our study thereby illustrates advantages in advancing\nthe design of mirror for rational engineering of light-matter interaction\nwithin deep-subwavelength-scaled optoelectronic devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Mar 2015 03:48:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-28"}
